pingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[10017,1420],"id":"38141eb9-a51e-42b3-8edc-1b31c7d85847","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf06744-document`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Read Recent from Notion","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"b4346340-6c98-2721-afcb-05a3d9a0a8a7","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Read Recent from Notion\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"7a6df3d8-5d3c-6de0-8bc9-e31265978ff1","name":"Note: Read Recent from Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Trim to Digest Size","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"2d158b47-ceb0-8fe8-47d4-b7ffb0528af7","name":"Note: Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Trim to Digest Size\n\nCaps the stream at 15 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Content (AI)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"4f816e79-72c3-c8da-ced7-99dc2e0b31fe","name":"Note: Trim to Digest Size"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Content (AI)\n\nMap-reduce summarization chain — handles long content without blowing the context window.\n\nPorts: ①→ Post Digest to Twilio, Post Digest to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"2f246c3c-c7b2-cdf5-27b3-f0e59e3c6209","name":"Note: Summarize Content (AI)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Summarize Content (AI)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"6e2fe445-cbba-5a46-1657-06cdccb0a2a6","name":"Note: Anthropic Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Confirm All Sends · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,220],"id":"9180fa13-bb4f-79d3-9334-f75f99e7ae1f","name":"Note: Post Digest to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Confirm All Sends · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,730],"id":"d717505c-8e22-d72e-2e68-dccf519be0ea","name":"Note: Post Digest to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Confirm All Sends\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Archive Digest in Notion","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"38e0b88f-7bc3-da09-f68b-dedd9eb43afc","name":"Note: Confirm All Sends"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Digest in Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fingerprint for Idempotency · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"5af26491-a090-e53f-c1cd-f2c02ee4d7d9","name":"Note: Archive Digest in Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per document (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"05a32ac3-4065-66ab-bbde-a13b24769f18","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"384c7edf-717a-bf9e-37a1-285a918bfa56","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"7f108305-cfdb-3d3e-e2f5-bafb90ff1cf1","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"4a92bee7-ee77-b4aa-51fe-87869fd3cb9e","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"5bc50366-567f-5197-baeb-a2a2ed65bb45","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5421,520],"id":"7d1ef6ab-5f50-020b-94c1-ebf97ffb72a2","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5745,520],"id":"29ebaeba-5067-4db2-5278-e4e80aceb149","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6069,520],"id":"dd2a759d-233f-39ea-8be9-cb2740c73538","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6393,520],"id":"34b136a5-32a3-c476-6bac-b9dacf0b905f","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6717,520],"id":"5b02845b-286b-c1e1-24c3-4bb3a250a60f","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7041,520],"id":"ce688409-58bb-1c4a-8d6e-ec5c3b244f1f","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7365,520],"id":"19904ff0-9499-22aa-415c-eface5a97bd3","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Sort Documents Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7689,520],"id":"85c108c6-61e7-781d-ad2e-bfb51b9e6b0d","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Documents Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8013,520],"id":"a02b02e0-ebd0-0a69-5f2a-402c79fa8529","name":"Note: Sort Documents Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8337,520],"id":"12fcc1ff-8a01-3573-b739-380c74f6150e","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8661,520],"id":"8d210a51-91e0-d36c-e185-071b0b3b61fa","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8985,520],"id":"8eec8f12-f4d1-ae10-fc49-2919cdf62354","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9309,520],"id":"a3e41408-9811-f1a0-1256-54e6ed7094ae","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Twilio · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9633,520],"id":"2674556d-66c9-611e-1367-502f2bc5660b","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9957,520],"id":"59bf611f-d801-4364-d50d-7e067f10186e","name":"Note: Send Summary to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Twilio","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9309,1540],"id":"ffab3e8e-eef2-853f-e228-851c8982b8b3","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9633,1540],"id":"99bd8250-8ca6-0ec6-5d1b-8995bf1b89ce","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9957,1540],"id":"ffae2294-8dec-2b6c-bffa-e161851f7c42","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Digest long emails with Google Sheets and Twilio\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDigest long emails with Google Sheets and Twilio. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual document search is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Read Recent from Notion → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Post Digest to Twilio → Confirm All Sends → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating document search in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Anthropic API key; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"4d7a7992-083e-e507-12d3-21bce8b1152e","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-320],"id":"fa98b88e-9408-6114-317c-e076427b8f6d","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-320],"id":"5c790b13-174c-d5c7-f077-85fe8796e3a5","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-320],"id":"6d979b10-c288-aceb-08d7-4c83d59b97ca","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your document search process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-320],"id":"6d6c3d99-9d00-0096-33ab-1b6f07c06784","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Recent from Notion","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Recent from Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Newest First","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Trim to Digest Size","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Trim to Digest Size":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Anthropic Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Summarize Content (AI)":{"main":[[{"node":"Post Digest to Twilio","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Post Digest to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Twilio":{"main":[[{"node":"Confirm All Sends","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Confirm All Sends","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Confirm All Sends":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Digest in Notion","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Digest in Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Documents Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Documents Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Twilio":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Twilio":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"59757f67-7436-44c6-b4f0-ae2fb5803f10","id":"FDX06744"}